Name: Junglex
About the game: Rex got lost in this hostile jungle! Help him finish the levels and leave this place! Junglex is a platform game with a high level of difficulty that will put your nerves to the test! Can you get out of this jungle? Features: ■ 100 different levels! ■ 2 different biomes! ■ Many enemies and boss! ■ Difficult! ■ Addictive!
